Installing virtual env : 
	sudo apt-get install python3.4-venv
To create virtual env : 
	python3 -m venv myvenv
To use virtual env : 
	bujji@bujji:~/python/django$ source myvenv/bin/activate
After activating the same we'll get command line like this:
	(myvenv) bujji@bujji:~/python/django$ 
To dectivate or move out of virtual env:
	(myvenv) bujji@bujji:deactivate
	<=> Above shell converted like below
	bujji@bujji:~/python/django$
